#######################
### Token Operations
#######################

### Generate Token Approval Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/tokens/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chain": "optimism",
  "owner": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0",
  "tokenIdentifier": "USDC", 
  "spender": "0x1111111111111111111111111111111111111111",
  "amount": "1000.50"
}

#######################
### Aave Operations (Beta v0)
#######################

### Supply Asset to Aave (Optimism Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/beta/v0/aave/supply/optimism
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0",
  "call_data": {
    "asset": "USDC", 
    "amount": 100.5,
    "on_behalf_of": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0"
  }
}

###

### Withdraw Asset from Aave (Base Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/beta/v0/aave/withdraw/base
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0",
  "call_data": {
    "asset": "WETH", 
    "amount": 0.1,
    "on_behalf_of": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0"
  }
}

###

### Borrow Asset from Aave (Arbitrum Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/beta/v0/aave/borrow/arbitrum
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0",
  "call_data": {
    "asset": "DAI", 
    "amount": 50,
    "on_behalf_of": "0x552008c0f6870c2f77e5cC1d2eb9bdff03e30Ea0"
  }
}

###

### Repay Borrowed Asset to Aave (Optimism Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/beta/v0/aave/repay/optimism
Content-Type: application/json

{
